missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/selector.md:16:Chain 02 stays second because it is the strongest remaining genuinely geometric branch and has a high-quality failure mode. Its structure is disciplined: it separates Beltrami alignment, direction coherence, and tube persistence, then forces an early confrontation with the full stretching term rather than allowing descriptive vortex language to substitute for control.
