missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:47:This concern is real but not fatal. The project already knows that the vorticity route hits the same `beta = 4/3` barrier and that Beltrami cancellation is fragile. Retesting those directions is only justified if the refined chain states exactly what new localized estimate, commutator accounting, or Tao-relevant comparison is being added.
