+
+## Constraints
+
+- Use local repository materials only.
+- Be explicit about which parts of the Tao screen are `[VERIFIED]` from local texts and which are `[INFERRED]` extensions to the geometry route.
+- Do not move into final observable design, localization protocol, or kernel-level decomposition.
+- Do not count local control of `u x omega` or another local fragment as if it were already control of full stretching.
+
+## Deliverables
